name: J.I the Prince of NY
description: '''Justin Irvin Rivera''' (born September 23, 2001), better known by his stage name '''J.I the Prince of N.Y''' or more recently simply '''J.I.''', is an American rapper, singer, and songwriter. He is best known for his 2019 breakout single "[[Need Me (J.I the Prince of N.Y song)|Need Me]]", which has over 100 million streams on [[Spotify]].{{facts|date=January 2023}}
